{
  "name": "Stream-End Gratitude, Farewells & Credits — Example Sequence",
  "description": "Example setups for the **Stream-End Gratitude, Farewells & Credits** script.\n\nImports two preset effect lists plus a **Credits Ended** return handler:\n- **Stream End Sequence** — the live sequence: Generate credits → set the OBS browser source URL → change to the credits scene → post the Discord gratitude summary → show the farewell.\n- **Stream End Sequence (OFFLINE Test)** — the same credits reveal with **no Discord message and no farewell**, pre-loaded with sample credits, so you can test safely without going live or posting to a Discord server.\n\nThe import asks for your OBS source/scene names (defaults match the install guide). You can also pick these from the live dropdowns inside each effect after import. For the live sequence you must select your Discord channel on the Send Discord Message effect and replace the farewell HTML. See docs/INSTALL.md.",
  "version": 1,
  "author": "goproslowyo",
